---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="TDEE Calculator"
  description="Calculate your TDEE (Total Daily Energy Expenditure) in 30 seconds. Find your maintenance calories and ideal calorie deficit for sustainable weight loss."
  canonical="https://loganhealth.co.uk/tdee"
  keywords="TDEE calculator, total daily energy expenditure, calorie calculator, weight loss, calorie deficit, Logan Health"
  ogTitle="TDEE Calculator - Total Daily Energy Expenditure | Logan Health"
  ogDescription="Calculate your TDEE (Total Daily Energy Expenditure) in 30 seconds. Find your maintenance calories and ideal calorie deficit for sustainable weight loss."
  scripts={['/js/tdee.js']}
>
    <Fragment slot="head">
        <script is:inline type="application/ld+json">
        {
            "@context": "https://schema.org",
            "@type": "WebApplication",
            "name": "TDEE Calculator",
            "description": "Calculate your Total Daily Energy Expenditure (TDEE) and find your ideal calorie deficit for sustainable weight loss.",
            "url": "https://loganhealth.co.uk/tdee.html",
            "applicationCategory": "HealthApplication",
            "operatingSystem": "Any",
            "offers": {
                "@type": "Offer",
                "price": "0",
                "priceCurrency": "GBP"
            },
            "provider": {
                "@type": "Organization",
                "name": "Logan Health",
                "url": "https://loganhealth.co.uk"
            }
        }
        </script>
    </Fragment>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="section" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-dark) 0%, var(--color-primary) 100%); color: var(--color-white); padding-top: 120px; padding-bottom: var(--spacing-8);">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header" style="text-align: center;">
                <span class="section-tag" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color: var(--color-white);">Free Calculator</span>
                <h1 class="section-title" style="color: var(--color-white); font-size: var(--font-size-4xl);">Calculate Your TDEE in 30 Seconds</h1>
                <p class="section-subtitle" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">Find your maintenance calories and ideal calorie deficit for weight loss using the Logan Health free TDEE calculator.</p>

                <div class="tdee-hero-benefits" style="justify-content: center;">
                    <span class="tdee-hero-benefit">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M13.333 4L6 11.333 2.667 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                        Personalised calorie target
                    </span>
                    <span class="tdee-hero-benefit">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M13.333 4L6 11.333 2.667 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                        Designed for sustainable fat loss
                    </span>
                    <span class="tdee-hero-benefit">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M13.333 4L6 11.333 2.667 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                        Trusted by GLP-1 weight loss patients
                    </span>
                </div>

                <a href="#tdee-calculator" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">Calculate My TDEE</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Most Diets Fail -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">Why Most Diets Fail</h2>
                <p style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);">Most people start dieting without knowing how many calories their body actually needs.</p>
                <p style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);">Without this number, weight loss becomes guesswork.</p>
                <p>Your body burns calories through:</p>
                <ul style="list-style: disc; padding-left: var(--spacing-6); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">
                    <li>Metabolism</li>
                    <li>Daily movement</li>
                    <li>Exercise</li>
                    <li>Digestion</li>
                </ul>
                <p style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);">This total is called your <strong>TDEE (Total Daily Energy Expenditure)</strong>.</p>
                <p>Understanding it is the first step to sustainable weight loss.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What Is TDEE? -->
    <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-bg-alt);">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <span class="section-tag">What Is TDEE</span>
                <h2 class="section-title">What Is TDEE?</h2>
                <p style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);">TDEE stands for <strong>Total Daily Energy Expenditure</strong>.</p>
                <p style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);">It represents the total number of calories your body burns each day.</p>
                <p>Your TDEE depends on several factors:</p>
                <ul style="list-style: disc; padding-left: var(--spacing-6); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">
                    <li>Age</li>
                    <li>Height</li>
                    <li>Weight</li>
                    <li>Activity level</li>
                    <li>Muscle mass</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Knowing this number allows you to:</p>
                <div class="difference-grid">
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p><strong>Maintain weight</strong> by eating at your TDEE</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p><strong>Lose fat</strong> by eating below your TDEE</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p><strong>Gain muscle</strong> by eating above your TDEE</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TDEE Calculator -->
    <section class="section" id="tdee-calculator">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="tdee-calculator-card">
                <span class="section-tag" style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3); display: inline-block;">Calculator</span>
                <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8);">Calculate Your TDEE</h2>
                <!-- Age -->
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="form-label" for="tdeeAge">Age</label>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <input type="number" id="tdeeAge" class="form-input" placeholder="Your age" min="18" max="100">
                        <span class="input-suffix">years</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Sex -->
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="form-label">Sex</label>
                    <div class="radio-group horizontal">
                        <label class="radio-option">
                            <input type="radio" name="tdeeSex" value="male">
                            <span class="radio-label">Male</span>
                        </label>
                        <label class="radio-option">
                            <input type="radio" name="tdeeSex" value="female">
                            <span class="radio-label">Female</span>
                        </label>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Height -->
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="form-label">Height</label>
                    <div class="unit-toggle">
                        <button type="button" class="unit-btn active" data-unit="metric" data-target="tdeeHeight">cm</button>
                        <button type="button" class="unit-btn" data-unit="imperial" data-target="tdeeHeight">ft/in</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-row" id="tdeeHeightMetric">
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <input type="number" id="tdeeHeightCm" class="form-input" placeholder="Your height in cm" min="110" max="234">
                            <span class="input-suffix">cm</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-row hidden" id="tdeeHeightImperial" style="display: none;">
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <input type="number" id="tdeeHeightFt" class="form-input" placeholder="Feet" min="3" max="7">
                            <span class="input-suffix">ft</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <input type="number" id="tdeeHeightIn" class="form-input" placeholder="Inches" min="0" max="11">
                            <span class="input-suffix">in</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Weight -->
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="form-label">Weight</label>
                    <div class="unit-toggle">
                        <button type="button" class="unit-btn active" data-unit="metric" data-target="tdeeWeight">kg</button>
                        <button type="button" class="unit-btn" data-unit="imperial" data-target="tdeeWeight">st/lbs</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-row" id="tdeeWeightMetric">
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <input type="number" id="tdeeWeightKg" class="form-input" placeholder="Your weight in kg" min="30" max="300" step="0.1">
                            <span class="input-suffix">kg</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-row hidden" id="tdeeWeightImperial" style="display: none;">
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <input type="number" id="tdeeWeightSt" class="form-input" placeholder="Stone" min="4" max="47">
                            <span class="input-suffix">st</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <input type="number" id="tdeeWeightLbs" class="form-input" placeholder="Pounds" min="0" max="13" step="0.1">
                            <span class="input-suffix">lbs</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Activity Level -->
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="form-label" for="tdeeActivityLevel">Activity Level</label>
                    <select id="tdeeActivityLevel" class="form-select">
                        <option value="">Select your activity level</option>
                        <option value="sedentary">Sedentary - Little or no exercise, desk job</option>
                        <option value="lightly-active">Lightly Active - Light exercise 1-3 days/week</option>
                        <option value="moderately-active">Moderately Active - Moderate exercise 3-5 days/week</option>
                        <option value="very-active">Very Active - Hard exercise 6-7 days/week</option>
                        <option value="extra-active">Extra Active - Very hard exercise, physical job</option>
                    </select>
                </div>

                <!-- Calculate Button -->
                <button class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg btn-block" id="tdeeCalculateBtn">Calculate My TDEE</button>

                <!-- Results -->
                <div class="tdee-results" id="tdeeResults" style="display: none;">
                    <div class="tdee-result-card tdee-maintenance">
                        <span class="tdee-result-label">Maintenance Calories</span>
                        <span class="tdee-result-value" id="tdeeMaintenance">--</span>
                        <span class="tdee-result-unit">kcal / day</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tdee-result-card tdee-deficit">
                        <span class="tdee-result-label">Fat Loss Range</span>
                        <span class="tdee-result-value" id="tdeeDeficit">--</span>
                        <span class="tdee-result-unit">kcal / day</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Medicated Weight Loss -->
    <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-bg-alt);">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">Thinking of Using Medicated Weight Loss?</h2>
                <p style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);">GLP-1 medication such as Mounjaro and Wegovy assist with reducing appetite and help people eat fewer calories.</p>
                <p style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);">However, fat loss still requires a calorie deficit.</p>
                <p>Calculating your TDEE helps you understand:</p>
                <ul style="list-style: disc; padding-left: var(--spacing-6); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">
                    <li>How much you should eat</li>
                    <li>Whether you are in a calorie deficit</li>
                    <li>How to avoid weight loss plateaus</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Calculate Your TDEE? -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-wrapper" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title">Why Calculate Your TDEE?</h2>
                <p>When you know your TDEE you can:</p>
                <div class="difference-grid" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-6);">
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p><strong>Create a sustainable calorie deficit</strong></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p><strong>Avoid overly restrictive diets</strong></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p><strong>Maintain muscle while losing fat</strong></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="difference-icon">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p><strong>Track progress more accurately</strong></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="section" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-dark) 0%, var(--color-primary) 100%); color: var(--color-white);">
        <div class="container">
            <div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--color-white); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);">Want Medical Support for Weight Loss?</h2>
                <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-size: var(--font-size-lg); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">Logan Health offers clinician-led weight loss programmes, including support for patients using GLP-1 medications.</p>
                <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);">Our team helps you:</p>
                <div class="difference-grid" style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8); max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" style="flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--color-white); margin-top: 2px;">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); margin: 0;">Optimise nutrition</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" style="flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--color-white); margin-top: 2px;">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); margin: 0;">Manage medication safely</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="difference-item">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" style="flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--color-white); margin-top: 2px;">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); margin: 0;">Achieve sustainable weight loss</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">With Logan Health you get the support you need on a medicated weight loss journey, including:</p>
                <ul style="text-align: left; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-8); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--spacing-3);">
                    <li style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--spacing-3);">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M13.333 4L6 11.333 2.667 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                        Regular check-ins with our healthcare team
                    </li>
                    <li style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--spacing-3);">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M13.333 4L6 11.333 2.667 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                        Over 500 GLP-1 friendly recipes
                    </li>
                    <li style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--spacing-3);">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M13.333 4L6 11.333 2.667 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                        Meal planning based on your TDEE and preferences
                    </li>
                    <li style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--spacing-3);">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M13.333 4L6 11.333 2.667 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                        Tracking app to log progress and side effects
                    </li>
                    <li style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--spacing-3);">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M13.333 4L6 11.333 2.667 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                        Fat loss calculator
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <p style="color: var(--color-white); font-size: var(--font-size-lg); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">Ready to take the next step?</p>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--spacing-4); justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                    <a href="index.html#questionnaire" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">Check Your Eligibility</a>
                    <a href="index.html#contact" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: var(--color-white); border: 2px solid var(--color-white);">Contact Us</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
